  <summary date="2006-11-07T22:33:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Victim-Activated Landmine Abolition Act of 2006 - Expresses the sense of Congress that the government should continue to set an example for other countries by banning procurement of victim-activated landmines and other weapons designed to be victim-activated.

Prohibits the federal government from procuring such landmines or weapons in any circumstance.</summary>
